						               													<description>Fast tactical game, Chess like, set in Arthurian's mythology universe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will be commanding minions as you&amp;rsquo;ll be casting powerful spells to achieve victory. Special dice will help to control changing board every turn and power hexes give you cards for conducting key maneuvers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Goal of the game is to defeat opponent mage: Merlin or Mordred.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every turn you will draw a number of cards depends on how many power hexes your minions are controlling on the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cards in your hand are your actions. Spending them you can move your minions, you can boost attack skill or defenses and at last you can cast special spells, like: tornado, run or stone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every player at the beginning of their turn is forced to roll a special die which change an element on the board, making it different each turn. It is the player's choice when the turn ends whether or not he/she has any cards left on a hand or not.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In a tournament version you can use a Chess Clock for a fast and full of emotion game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
